	+ commit 0adaf7bafd352f1c3a1e797493780150e3bb0adc
	* NEWS: mention interface change.
	* lang/cpp/src/key.cpp (Key::origin, Key::lastUpdate): New.
	* lang/cpp/src/key.h (Key::Origin): New enum.

